474|source=non}}||{{Commons-inline|Category:Stained-glass windows of the side aisles of Cath\u00e9drale Notre-Dame de Chartres baie 045|Baie 45}}\n|-\n|47||Histoire de No\u00e9||Les charpentiers, charrons et tonneliers||1205-1215<br>Restaur\u00e9e en 1924 par Gaudin,<br>puis dans les ann\u00e9es 1980||{{Base Palissy|IM28000473|source=non}}||{{Commons-inline|Category:Stained-glass windows of the side aisles of Cath\u00e9drale Notre-Dame de Chartres baie 047|Baie 47}}\n|}\n--->\n<gallery mode=\"packed\" heights=\"200\" caption=\"Details of Bays 37, 41, 43 and 45\">\nChartres - Vitrail de la Symbolique de la Passion -4.JPG|Bay 37<br>Typological Passion (Descent from the Cross).\nChartres - Vitrail de la Vie de Joseph.JPG|Bay 41<br>Life of Joseph.\nChartres - Vitrail de la Vie de saint Eustache -1.JPG|Bay 43<br>Life of Saint Eustace\nChartres - Vitrail de la Vie de saint Lubin-1.jpg|Bay 45<br>Life of Saint Lubin.\n</gallery>\n\n=== \"Lives\" windows ===\n<!---\n{|class=\"wikitable alternance\" style=\"width:100%;text-align:center;font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n! N\u00b0 baie !! Nom du vitrail !! Donateurs !! Dates !! Base Palissy !! Wikimedia Commons\n|-\n| 0 || [[Vitrail des Ap\u00f4tres \u00e0 Chartres|Histoire des Ap\u00f4tres]] || Les boulangers || 1210-1225 || {{Base Palissy|IM28000390|source=non}} || {{Commons-inline|Category:Stained-glass windows of the ambulatory of Cath\u00e9drale Notre-Dame de Chartres baie 000|Baie 0}}\n|-\n| 1 || Histoire de saint Simon et de saint Jude || Le chanoine Henri Noblet || 1220-1225 || {{Base Palissy|IM28000399|source=non}} || {{Commons-inline|Category:Stained-glass windows of the ambulatory of Cath\u00e9drale Notre-Dame de Chartres baie 001|Baie 1}}\n|-\n| 2 || Histoire de saint Andr\u00e9 || - || 1210-1225 || {{Base Palissy|IM28000398|source=non}} || {{Commons-inline|Category:Stained-glass windows of the ambulatory of Cath\u00e9drale Notre-Dame de Chartres baie 002|Baie 2}}\n|-\n| 3 || Grisaille || - || {{s-|XIII}} || {{Base Palissy|PM28